6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qwpy9kqzmezz-1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>他们不仅从虚拟“快速变身”为实体，还展示了多种多样的表演，比如两人并肩唱歌、添加虚拟版本的自己（？）、来来去去等。在舞台上。 。</p><p>引起我注意的是长濑由香（实体）向观众走来唱歌的剪影，当她回到透明LED的另一边时，她融入了长濑由香和她的朋友们（虚拟）的剪影他们在舞台上走来走去。有一个场景，我有一瞬间看不到他。这是我第一次体验“三维空间中存在的人物消失在图像中”，这是一种奇怪的感觉。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.1usu642mhsax-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.628i89jg6fjo-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e5313